c: 2
v: 91
t: "And when it is said to them (the Jews), \"Believe in what Allah has sent down,\" they say, \"We believe in what was sent down to us.\" And they disbelieve in that which came after it, while it is the truth confirming what is with them. Say (O Muhammad to them): \"Why then have you killed the Prophets of Allah aforetime, if you indeed have been believers"